<main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-7">
  <h1 class="font-bold text-lg md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl">Buat Modul Ajar secara cepat dan efisien<br/>dengan bantuan teknologi berbasis AI (Akal Imitasi)</h1>
  <p>Program ini dirancang untuk mempermudah proses pembuatan modul ajar dengan bantuan teknologi berbasis AI. Perlu diingat bahwa hasil yang dihasilkan oleh AI mungkin perlu diperiksa kembali untuk memastikan keakuratan dan kecocokan dengan konteks pendidikan Anda.</p>

  <div class="mt-10 border-2 md:border-4 border-dashed p-5">
    <b>Gunakan template dibawah ini untuk mempermudah proses pembuatan modul ajar:</b>
    <div class="flex" id="templateButtonsContainer">

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10 border-2 md:border-4 border-dashed p-5">
    <div class="text-gray-700">
      <p>Tolong isi beberapa kolom dibawah ini untuk membantu AI membuat dokumen.</p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1 font-bold mt-1">
        Gunakan tombol
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-400 border border-gray-500 p-1 rounded">
          <%- include('components/icons/bsstars.ejs', {width: "16px", height: "16px"}) %>
        </span>
        untuk menyempurnakan kalimat dengan bantuan AI.
      </div>
    </div>

    <form id="rppForm" method="post" class="mt-5">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-10 w-full">

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="namaSekolah" id="namaSekolahWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-sky-800">Satuan Pendidikan</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Boleh dikosongkan</small>
          
          <input type="text" name="namaSekolah" id="namaSekolah" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-sky-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: SDN 1 Cibodas">
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="namaPenyusun" id="namaPenyusunWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-green-800">Nama Penyusun</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Boleh dikosongkan</small>
          
          <input type="text" name="namaPenyusun" id="namaPenyusun" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-green-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: Budi Santoso">
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="nip" id="nipWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-amber-800">NIP</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Boleh dikosongkan</small>
          
          <input type="text" name="nip" id="nip" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-amber-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: 1234567890">
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="fase" id="faseWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-orange-800">Fase</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Pilih Fase yang sesuai</small>
          
          <select name="fase" id="fase" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-orange-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-800 focus:border-transparent appearance-none cursor-pointer" required>
            <option value="Fondasi" selected>Fondasi</option>
          </select>
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="semester" id="semesterWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-red-800">Semester</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Semester saat ini</small>
          
          <input type="number" name="semester" id="semester" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-red-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: 2" min="1" max="14" required>
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="bulan" id="bulanWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-pink-800">Bulan</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Pilih bulan pelaksanaan</small>
          
          <select name="bulan" id="bulan" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-pink-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-pink-800 focus:border-transparent appearance-none cursor-pointer" required>
            <option value="Januari" selected>Januari</option>
            <option value="Februari">Februari</option>
            <option value="Maret">Maret</option>
            <option value="April">April</option>
            <option value="Mei">Mei</option>
            <option value="Juni">Juni</option>
            <option value="Juli">Juli</option>
            <option value="Agustus">Agustus</option>
            <option value="September">September</option>
            <option value="Oktober">Oktober</option>
            <option value="November">November</option>
            <option value="Desember">Desember</option>
          </select>
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="mingguKe" id="mingguKeWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-purple-800">Minggu Ke</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Minggu ke berapa dalam pembelajaran kali ini</small>
          
          <input type="number" name="mingguKe" id="mingguKe" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-purple-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: 2" min="1" max="4" required>
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="kelas" id="kelasWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-violet-800">Kelas</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Pilih Kelas yang sesuai</small>
          
          <select name="kelas" id="kelas" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-violet-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-violet-800 focus:border-transparent appearance-none cursor-pointer" required>
            <option value="Kelompok A (4-5 tahun)" selected>Kelompok A (4-5 tahun)</option>
            <option value="Kelompok B (5-6 tahun)">Kelompok B (5-6 tahun)</option>
          </select>
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="jumlahAnak" id="jumlahAnakWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-indigo-800">Jumlah Anak</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Boleh dikosongkan</small>
          
          <input type="number" name="jumlahAnak" id="jumlahAnak" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-indigo-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: 10">
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="alokasiWaktu1" id="alokasiWaktu1Wrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-rose-800">Alokasi Waktu</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Hari &times; Jam Pelajaran</small>
          
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <input type="hidden" name="alokasiWaktu" id="alokasiWaktu" required>

            <input type="number" id="alokasiWaktu1"
            class="w-10 aspect-square border-2 border-rose-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-rose-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="5" oninput="handleAlokasiWaktuChange()" required>
            <span>&times;</span>
            <input type="number" id="alokasiWaktu2" 
            class="w-10 aspect-square border-2 border-rose-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-rose-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="10" oninput="handleAlokasiWaktuChange()" required>
            <span class="font-semibold mt-2 text-rose-800">JP</span>
          </div>
          
        </label>

        <div class="group block" id="temaSubtemaWrapper">
          <label for="temaSubtema" class="cursor-pointer">
            <p class="font-semibold text-sky-800">Tema/Subtema</p>
            <small class="block text-gray-500">Tema dan Subtema yang akan diajarkan</small>
          </label>

          <div class="relative mt-2 flex items-center border-2 border-sky-800/50 rounded-md transition-all focus-within:border-sky-800 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-sky-800/50">
            <input 
              type="text" 
              name="temaSubtema" 
              id="temaSubtema"
              class="w-full border-none bg-transparent p-2.5 text-gray-700 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none" 
              placeholder="Contoh: Keluarga / Keluargaku Sayang" required>

            <div class="flex items-center pr-3">
              <%- include('components/ai.ejs', { type: "ai.temaSubtema", prompt: "Tulis tema dan subtema yang akan diajarkan. Contoh: Diriku/Identitasku" }) %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block cursor-pointer" id="modelPembelajaranWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-orange-800">Model Pembelajaran</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Pilih satu atau lebih pendekatan yang sesuai</small>

          <input type="hidden" name="modelPembelajaran" id="modelPembelajaran" required>

          <div class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-orange-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-orange-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="modelPembelajaranKolaboratif" class="model-pembelajaran-option accent-orange-800" value="Kolaboratif">
              <span>Kolaboratif</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-orange-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-orange-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="modelPembelajaranEksperimental" class="model-pembelajaran-option accent-orange-800" value="Eksperimental">
              <span>Eksperimental</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-orange-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-orange-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="modelPembelajaranBermainPeran" class="model-pembelajaran-option accent-orange-800" value="Bermain Peran">
              <span>Bermain Peran</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-orange-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-orange-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="modelPembelajaranDiscoveryLearning" class="model-pembelajaran-option accent-orange-800" value="Discovery Learning">
              <span>Discovery Learning</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-orange-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-orange-50 sm:col-span-2">
              <input type="checkbox" id="modelPembelajaranPjBL" class="model-pembelajaran-option accent-orange-800" value="Project-Based Learning (PjBL)">
              <span>Project-Based Learning (PjBL)</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block cursor-pointer" id="elemenCpWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-green-800">Pilih Elemen CP</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Pilih satu atau lebih elemen Capaian Pembelajaran Fase Fondasi</small>

          <input type="hidden" name="elemenCp" id="elemenCp">

          <div class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-green-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-green-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="elemenCpAgama" class="elemen-cp-option accent-green-800" value="Nilai Agama dan Budi Pekerti">
              <span>Nilai Agama dan Budi Pekerti</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-green-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-green-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="elemenCpJatiDiri" class="elemen-cp-option accent-green-800" value="Jati Diri">
              <span>Jati Diri</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-green-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-green-50 sm:col-span-2">
              <input type="checkbox" id="elemenCpLiterasiSains" class="elemen-cp-option accent-green-800" value="Dasar-dasar Literasi, Matematika, Sains, Teknologi, Rekayasa, dan Seni">
              <span>Literasi-Sains-Seni</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block cursor-pointer" id="dimensiProfilLulusanWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-purple-800">Dimensi Profil Lulusan</p>
          <small class="text-gray-500">Pilih dimensi profil lulusan yang relevan</small>

          <input type="hidden" name="dimensiProfilLulusan" id="dimensiProfilLulusan">

          <div class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl1" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL1 Keimanan dan Ketakwaan">
              <span>DPL1 Keimanan dan Ketakwaan</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl2" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL2 Kewargaan">
              <span>DPL2 Kewargaan</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl3" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL3 Penalaran Kritis">
              <span>DPL3 Penalaran Kritis</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl4" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL4 Kreativitas">
              <span>DPL4 Kreativitas</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl5" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL5 Kolaborasi">
              <span>DPL5 Kolaborasi</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl6" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL6 Kemandirian">
              <span>DPL6 Kemandirian</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl7" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL7 Kesehatan">
              <span>DPL7 Kesehatan</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl8" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL8 Komunikasi">
              <span>DPL8 Komunikasi</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block md:col-span-2" id="materiPembelajaranWrapper">
          <label for="materiPembelajaran" class="cursor-pointer">
            <p class="font-semibold text-blue-800">Materi Pembelajaran</p>
            <small class="block text-gray-500">Deskripsikan dengan singkat materi yang akan diajarkan</small>
          </label>

          <div class="relative mt-2 rounded-md border-2 border-blue-800/50 transition-all focus-within:border-blue-800 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-blue-800/50">
            <textarea
              name="materiPembelajaran"
              id="materiPembelajaran"
              rows="3"
              class="w-full resize-y border-none bg-transparent p-2.5 pr-12 text-gray-700 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none"
              placeholder="Contoh: Materi pengenalan anggota keluarga mencakup ..." required></textarea>

            <div class="absolute right-3 top-3 flex items-center">
              <%- include('components/ai.ejs', {type: "ai.materiPembelajaran", prompt: "Deskripsikan dengan singkat materi yang akan diajarkan"}) %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block md:col-span-2" id="identifikasiPesertaDidikWrapper">
          <label for="identifikasiPesertaDidik" class="cursor-pointer">
            <p class="font-semibold text-green-800">Identifikasi Peserta Didik</p>
            <small class="block text-gray-500">Deskripsikan karakteristik dan perkembangan peserta didik</small>
          </label>

          <div class="relative mt-2 rounded-md border-2 border-green-800/50 transition-all focus-within:border-green-800 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-green-800/50">
            <textarea
              name="identifikasiPesertaDidik"
              id="identifikasiPesertaDidik"
              rows="3"
              class="w-full resize-y border-none bg-transparent p-2.5 pr-12 text-gray-700 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none"
              placeholder="Contoh: Anak memiliki kemampuan ..." required></textarea>

            <div class="absolute right-3 top-3 flex items-center">
              <%- include('components/ai.ejs', {type: "ai.identifikasiPesertaDidik", prompt: "Deskripsikan karakteristik dan perkembangan peserta didik"}) %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block md:col-span-2" id="tujuanPembelajaranWrapper">
          <label for="tujuanPembelajaran" class="cursor-pointer">
            <p class="font-semibold text-lime-800">Tujuan Pembelajaran</p>
            <small class="block text-gray-500">Tulis singkat 1-2 kalimat target pembelajaran</small>
          </label>

          <div class="relative mt-2 rounded-md border-2 border-lime-800/50 transition-all focus-within:border-lime-800 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-lime-800/50">
            <textarea
              name="tujuanPembelajaran"
              id="tujuanPembelajaran"
              rows="3"
              class="w-full resize-y border-none bg-transparent p-2.5 pr-12 text-gray-700 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none"
              placeholder="Contoh: Anak mampu menyebutkan anggota keluarganya..." required></textarea>

            <div class="absolute right-3 top-3 flex items-center">
              <%- include('components/ai.ejs', {type: "ai.tujuanPembelajaran", prompt: "Tulis apa yang ingin dicapai dalam pembelajaran ini?"}) %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block" id="topikPembelajaranWrapper">
          <label for="topikPembelajaran" class="cursor-pointer">
            <p class="font-semibold text-amber-800">Topik Pembelajaran</p>
            <small class="block text-gray-500">Topik pendek yang spesifik untuk pekan ini</small>
          </label>

          <div class="relative mt-2 flex items-center border-2 border-amber-800/50 rounded-md transition-all focus-within:border-amber-800 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-amber-800/50">
            <input
              type="text"
              name="topikPembelajaran"
              id="topikPembelajaran"
              class="w-full border-none bg-transparent p-2.5 text-gray-700 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none"
              placeholder="Contoh: Aku dan Lingkungan Sekitarku" required>

            <div class="flex items-center pr-3">
              <%- include('components/ai.ejs', {type: "ai.topikPembelajaran", prompt: "Tulis topik pembelajaran yang spesifik untuk pekan ini"}) %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block md:col-span-2" id="kegiatanDynamicWrapper">
          <p class="font-semibold text-violet-800">Kegiatan Harian</p>
          <small class="block text-gray-500">Kolom kegiatan akan otomatis dibuat berdasarkan Hari x JP pada Alokasi Waktu</small>

          <div id="kegiatanDynamicContainer" class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4"></div>
        </div>

        <template id="kegiatanAiButtonTemplate">
          <button type="button" class="bg-transparent border-0 p-0 m-0 cursor-pointer" title="AI: Sempurnakan kegiatan">
            <%- include('components/icons/bsstars.ejs', {width: "16px", height: "16px"}) %>
            <span class="sr-only">AI: Sempurnakan kegiatan</span>
          </button>
        </template>

      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 mt-5">
        <button id="deleteTemplateBtn" type="button" class="w-full px-4 py-2 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-700 focus:ring-offset-2" onclick="deleteExternalTemplate()">
          <span>Hapus Template</span>
        </button>

        <button id="saveTemplateBtn" type="button" class="w-full px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-700 focus:ring-offset-2" onclick="saveExternalTemplate()">
          <span>Simpan Template</span>
        </button>

        <button id="exportTemplateBtn" type="button" class="w-full px-4 py-2 bg-violet-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-violet-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-violet-700 focus:ring-offset-2" onclick="exportTemplate()">
          <span>Export Template</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <button id="rppFormSubmitBtn" type="submit" class="w-full mt-4 p-2 bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-green-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-700 focus:ring-offset-2">
        <span>Buat Dokumen</span>
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <template id="loadingGenerateWrapper">
    <div class="items-center gap-3 animate-pulse mt-2 flex">
      <img src="/images/loading-generate.gif" alt="Loading Animation" class="w-10 h-8">
      <span id="loading-generate-text"></span>
    </div>
  </template>

  <script src="/js/SwalWrapper.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/loading-indicator.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/home.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/home-template.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/dynamic-save-input.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/ai-auto-fill.js"></script>
</main>